ch.maybites.utils.dynlinker
Class DynFactory<ObjectType,CallbackType>

java.lang.Object
  ch.maybites.utils.dynlinker.DynFactory<ObjectType,CallbackType>
Type Parameters:
ObjectType - The Type of Object this Factory helps to create dynamic links to
CallbackType - The Type of Callback Object that helps to manipulate the linking party - usually the object that implements DynLinkRegistrar.
public class DynFactory<ObjectType,CallbackType>
extends java.lang.Object

The Dynamic Link Factory is a useful tool to manage dynamic instances that can appear and disappear because of asynchronous events. The inital impulse to create this library was to deal with the dynamic creation of MaxMSP mxj-objects that need to be linked with other mxj-objects. *

Author:
maybites
